.SH NAME
md_docs_2doxygen-awesome-css-2_84_82_2docs_2extensions \- Extensions 
.PP


.PP
In addition to the base theme provided by \fRdoxygen-awesome\&.css\fP, this repository comes with JavaScript extensions that require additional setup steps to get them running\&.

.PP
The extensions require customizations in the header HTML template\&. Here is how you can create the default template with Doxygen:

.PP
.IP "1." 4
Create default header template: 
.PP
.nf
doxygen \-w html header\&.html delete_me\&.html delete_me\&.css

.fi
.PP

.IP "2." 4
Reference the template in your \fRDoxyfile\fP: 
.PP
.nf
HTML_HEADER            = header\&.html

.fi
.PP

.PP

.PP
\fRMore details on header customization\fP
.SH "Dark Mode Toggle"
.PP
Adds a button next to the search bar to manually enable and disable the dark theme variant:

.PP

.PP

.PP
.SS "Installation"
.IP "1." 4
Add the required resources in your \fRDoxyfile\fP:
.IP "  \(bu" 4
\fBHTML_EXTRA_FILES:\fP \fRdoxygen-awesome-darkmode-toggle\&.js\fP
.IP "  \(bu" 4
\fBHTML_EXTRA_STYLESHEET:\fP \fRdoxygen-awesome-sidebar-only-darkmode-toggle\&.css\fP \fI(ONLY required for the sidebar-only theme variant!)\fP
.PP

.IP "2." 4
In the \fRheader\&.html\fP template, include \fRdoxygen-awesome-darkmode-toggle\&.js\fP at the end of the \fR<head>\fP and then initialize it: 
.PP
.nf
<html> 
    <head>
        <!\-\- \&.\&.\&. other metadata & script includes \&.\&.\&. \-\->
        <script type="text/javascript" src="$relpath^doxygen\-awesome\-darkmode\-toggle\&.js"></script>
        <script type="text/javascript">
            DoxygenAwesomeDarkModeToggle\&.init()
        </script>
    </head>
    <body>

.fi
.PP

.PP
.SS "Customizing"
Changing the tooltip of the button: 
.PP
.nf
DoxygenAwesomeDarkModeToggle\&.title = "Zwischen hellem/dunklem Modus wechseln"

.fi
.PP

.PP
Changing icons: Both Emoji and SVG icons are supported: 
.PP
